divs: sighting details[link moved to additional evidence section\cms\tg] more ufos from this night. i have observed them manipulating weather. this should be obvious to the astute observer. i have no reason to believe they are alien in nature, but appear to be spiritual in origin and makeup. you will notice they go from orb or fireball, to what appears to be a blinking aircraft. they are very numerous and can be seen directly above my home on any clear night. they have been a bit troublesome to have around, and occasionally come too close to comfort, but make for good video. thank you, ufozmankato
